"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1926711-Andy-Murray-Olympics-2024-retirement\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murraycould be denied the send-off he deserves at theOlympicsdespite confirming that he will retire after representing Great Britain in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9993232222948407, \"rank\": 0.0006555272045054645, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998100056654, \"rank\": 1.8999431712692205e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-oldannounced on Tuesday that he will be hanging up his racket after the Olympicsto bring the curtain down on his glittering career.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray was given a rousing reception in his final match atWimbledonearlier this month but it seems he will not receive a farewell ceremony at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.847894090039372e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tennis bosses have already confessed that their hands may be tied by the International Olympic Committee, who could prevent Murray from being given a fitting send-off.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.847894090039372e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Haggerty, president of the International Tennis Federation, said: \\\"I think we are in discussions with various players.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Haggerty_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9999516531302575, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Haggerty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Haggerty_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Haggerty_(tennis)\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Tennis Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot comes down to what they want and what they may think about, and often times we find that players do not want to talk about it at this moment and are not prepared.\\\"\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Speaking before Murray's final match atWimbledon, Haggerty suggested the ITF would need to convince Murray to play at the Davis Cup in order to give him the farewell ceremony he deserves.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.847894090039372e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999735956937816, \"rank\": 2.634894594217191e-05, \"text\": \"ITF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.847894090039372e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have had conversations regarding some of our other competitions, like the Davis Cup,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And you know, we'd like to work with the players and do something that they feel is appropriate and right.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I do not have the final answer for you on that, but we certainly would like to celebrate some of the legends of our game.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot will come down to, you know, what Andy himself would like to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Andy Murray claims 'mum Judy would kill me' if he copied Carlos Alcaraz  Do not miss:Paula Badosa speaks out after Tsitsipas relationship blamed for struggles  Do not miss:Nick Kyrgios exposed for having 'creepy' Rafael Nadal picture on his phone  ITF CEO Kelly Fairweather went on to explain that Olympic bosses are unlikely to grant permission for Murray to be honoured when he bows out in Paris, saying: \\\"If you are asking about Paris, we obviously fall under the direction of the IOC, and generally the IOC do not do that for any athlete across the Games.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.797595895784761e-40, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1741, \"end\": 1755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Badosa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paula Badosa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Badosa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Badosa\"}, {\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Kyrgios\", \"score\